  "texts": [
    "The VPME offers a policy evaluation toolkit, which enables the simulation and evaluation of the developed AI policies.",
    "In particular, it integrates different types of surveys based on different electronic channels.",
    "The surveys are linked to action strategies that can be implemented at different stages of an ML pipeline.",
    "A policymaker view and a stakeholder view are provided.",
    "Through their view, policymakers manage and create custom surveys, including application surveys and surveys in social media platforms such as Twitter (Figure 8)."
